oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Boy scouts at the Mule Day parade in Columbia
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of two boy scouts standing next to a car during the Mule Day parade in Columbia, Tennessee. Both of the boys are dressed in scout uniforms. Note: there is an object in the top left corner of the photograph creating an obstruction.
